            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "The code looks reasonable to me, so I consider it a bug that it doesn't work. My guess is that the `directive_locals` handling in the `AnalyseDeclarationsTransform` does not take (enough?) care about fused types.\r\n\r\nFurther investigation and PR welcome.",
